    <entry>
      <title>大学杂游</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/30/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E6%9D%82%E6%B8%B8/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/30/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E6%9D%82%E6%B8%B8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p><strong>如同每个最初来到大学这个陌生环境的普通人一样,大学最初的一个学期内充满了惊喜和回忆,我选择通过手中的手机拍摄的每一张照片记录下它们</strong></p><h3 id="正文"><a href="#正文" class="headerlink" title="正文"></a>正文</h3><p>  <strong>东门广场的花海01:</strong></p><p>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl4jET" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl4jET.md.jpg" alt="Jl4jET.md.jpg"></a><br>(每年的夏至秋季最盛,送走大四的毕业学长学姐,迎接初来驾到的小萌新们)</p><p>   <strong>东门广场的花海02:</strong></p><p>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl47gs" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl47gs.md.jpg" alt="Jl47gs.md.jpg"></a><br>(东理的荻花,应该是南昌比较有名的)</p><p> <strong>东门广场的花海03:</strong></p><p>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl454g" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl454g.md.jpg" alt="Jl454g.md.jpg"></a><br>  (靠近教学楼一边的景色,应该是我结束军训时拍摄的)</p><p>  <strong>东门广场的花海04:</strong></p><p>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl44US" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl44US.md.jpg" alt="Jl44US.md.jpg"></a><br>  (凑近了拍是这样的小花,不清楚什么品种,ps:没踩草皮(嘿嘿))</p><p>  <strong>东门广场的落日余晖:</strong></p><p>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl4T3j" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl4T3j.md.jpg" alt="Jl4T3j.md.jpg"></a><br>   (ps:有点像一只展翅的白鹤) </p><p> <strong>宿舍楼楼下:</strong></p><p>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl4oCQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl4oCQ.md.jpg" alt="Jl4oCQ.md.jpg"></a></p><p> <strong>宿舍楼阳台:</strong></p><p>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl4hE8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl4hE8.jpg" alt="Jl4hE8.jpg"></a><br>   (这是九楼嗷)</p><p>  <strong>图书馆教室:</strong></p><p>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl4quq" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl4quq.jpg" alt="Jl4quq.jpg"></a> </p><p>(旁边较矮的应该是地学楼吧,较高是核工楼,正在建设的我也忘了叫啥(假东理学生上线),下面的蓝色窗子的教学楼是软件楼(害,一点排面都没有))  </p><p><strong>操场</strong></p><p>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl4LD0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl4LD0.jpg" alt="Jl4LD0.jpg"></a></p><p>(草是假的草皮,后面在建的就是上面的那个新楼嗷)</p><h4 id="后记"><a href="#后记" class="headerlink" title="后记"></a>后记</h4><p>  快上课了就不想文案了,附上一张八一广场的图(嘿嘿)</p><p><strong>八一广场:</strong><br>  <a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Jl4Hvn" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/20/Jl4Hvn.jpg" alt="Jl4Hvn.jpg"></a></p><p> (上英语课去咯,溜了溜了) </p>]]></content>
      
      
      
